"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:50:38.000Z","msg":"非安全地帶"},{"pid":"4928ee7a0869c549c50eef7724fd3cd4b63fab55","tid":2492322,"uid":159440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:51:47.000Z","msg":"許志安 <br />\n<br />\n擁抱會說話<br />\n<br />\n作詞：姚若龍<br />\n作曲：林東松<br />\n<br />\n我的感情只怕說不清　也許應該直接把心跳給妳聽<br />\n閃躲不及是妳的眼睛　整顆心在剎那間臣服於愛情<br />\n我己經忍了太久的愛意　壓住了我的呼吸<br />\n卻怕突然講出愛妳、要妳、害妳嚇得想逃離<br />\n如果擁抱能夠代替所有言語　愛已經濃的烈的讓我無法喘息<br />\n喔～但願擁抱代替我告訴妳　妳是我笑了、醉了、痛了的原因<br />\n愛不該想太多事情　何不就任憑感覺悄悄帶領<br />\n請妳慢慢走入我懷裡　不要不放心<br />\n傾聽我最想說的一句　說我愛妳<br />\n<br />\n但youtube 已經搵唔到呢首"},{"pid":"f07ac6b6db55cfda782532b7aff561933655fa44","tid":2492322,"uid":284514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4468b3650b6e7c07e055cfb624f4bcb6cc8190c","tid":2492322,"uid":284514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:48:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NUTtGMIYtH8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNUTtGMIYtH8&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL6EbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=85b0c87c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NUTtGMIYtH8</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:51:52.000Z","msg":"但係而家聽返真係一點說服力都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6998d6c4bef214fb284e73c01252d66b4d26d28","tid":2492322,"uid":5642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:52:59.000Z","msg":"表情"},{"pid":"f26afbd086f9d059e119fa48facc06f222e4e1d4","tid":2492322,"uid":146556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:55:52.000Z","msg":"翻騰"},{"pid":"2193559eff571ae8e38289f8039b271cd3eb0e90","tid":2492322,"uid":55800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:56:19.000Z","msg":"新天地隻碟啲side cut都好聽<br />\n時代廣場 幪面 下半世 不愛不散"},{"pid":"174185537d8f236f10343eee743967f7bb15bdec","tid":2492322,"uid":374159,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"208881a23000c8e5148f2d80249bdae00a5b55f7","tid":2492322,"uid":112997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:38:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/em7JnHJUijw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fem7JnHJUijw&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL6EbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=7a348769\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/em7JnHJUijw</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知未簽收算熱門定冷門，不過真係好正<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fERiLOGk7Ng\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FfERiLOGk7Ng&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL6EbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=52717c56\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fERiLOGk7Ng</a><br />\n<br />\n呢首絕對係安仔嘅滄海遺珠，原來多年前已經預言左安心出行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:56:33.000Z","msg":"未簽收好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9896b5eeae1e74cce31950b1b5e1c68cd9c54ab0","tid":2492322,"uid":203365,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T06:00:06.000Z","msg":"睇咗成頁都冇一步一生<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e507cec3b6bccca3e597da26d5e9d4098c0b53","tid":2492322,"uid":141326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T06:01:37.000Z","msg":"佢啲慘情歌真係好正<br />\n<br />\n愈要去討好妳　愈會令妳更討厭 <br />\n愈要去花心血　或會拖多幾多年 <br />\n當愛壞了　原來一切徒然 <br />\n說得再好　送得多美　仍被妳不恥  <br />\n我　就算沒有甚麼的缺點 <br />\n就算用最華貴的誠意 <br />\n當妳不再想說　我願意 <br />\n恐怕只會得到妳討厭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n寧願妳裝起騙人面具　寧願妳推搪說疲累 <br />\n寧願不哼一句　我也不想知道　<br />\n其實妳另有一位愛侶  <br />\n只有我在呆望這家裡每個角落　<br />\n尤如圍城冷漠 即使妳沒有講出走真相　<br />\n若要公式的說謊　妳已經不必再講"},{"pid":"fface87226f186dc993b2877511bd9c39aae9fc4","tid":2492322,"uid":16087,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T06:04:52.000Z","msg":"暗戀的習慣"},{"pid":"032da13d771ad4fcf41765f576c0a1d4cdfe1b60","tid":2492322,"uid":170160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T06:12:34.000Z","msg":"愛你，你管不了是禍，未想是肥婆，淫我、辱我、逼我入廁所，做什麼...啊啊 !  <br />\n<br />\n#可能唱俾韓紅聽 <img src=\"/assets/face